description:
Have your own idea? Can't find the painting you want? Are you looking for a custom painting? Well, let's solve your problems.

Contact me at justinbenfaida@gmail.com to discuss your ideas for your painting first. We will go over sizes, ideas, and pricing.

After we agree on terms you may put through a $150 downpayment here, and pay the rest when the work is completed to your satisfaction.

Custom pieces may range anywhere from $250 - $550 depending on needs, size, and detail.
